import React from 'react'
import { Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import "./style.css"
import "./component/navbar/navstyle.css"
import Dashborad from "./component/dashboard/Dashborad"
import Userprofile from "./component/userprofile/Userprofile"
import Student_Table  from "./component/table/Student_Table" 
import Loginuse from './component/login/Loginuse'
// import Insert from "./component/form/Insert"
import "./component/login/loginuser.css"
import Navbar from './component/Navbar'
const App = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <Routes >
        <Route path="/" element={<Loginuse/>}/>
        <Route element={<Navbar/>}>
            <Route path="dashborad" element={<Dashborad />}/>
            <Route  path="student" element={<Userprofile />}>
                   {/* <Route path="insert" element={<Insert />}/> */}
            </Route>
            <Route path="tablelist" element={<Student_Table />}/>
           
           
        </Route>
        </Routes> 
    </>
  )
}
export default App
